OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight, the odd
OL,7,Fshower in the northwest. Persistent
OL,8,Frain will spread into the northwest
OL,9,Flater in the night. Clear spells in
OL,10,Fthe east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy with rain spreading
OL,13,Fsoutheast across all parts, lingering
OL,14,Finto the afternoon in the east.
OL,15,FTurning drier in the north and west
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon. A colder day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
